title: Week 8 Live Football and Softball Updates
text: Missouri volleyball coaches release third statewide rankings Nixa and Ozark remain atop their classes in the third statewide Missouri Volleyball Coaches Association poll. In all there are eight area teams ranked across the four classes. Full Rankings: Class 1 1. Santa Fe 2. Winona 3. North Platte 4. New Haven 5. Oct. 7 Volleyball Power Rankings Keep in mind; the rankings are based on dominance by class.
